channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: NBA Unveils New Logo For Emirates NBA Cup
item.description: The NBA recently unveiled a new logo for the Emirates NBA Cup, the league’s second annual in-season tournament that will culminate with the championship game at T-Mobile Arena in Las Vegas on Dec. 17.

item.description: Virginia Tech unveiled new uniforms on Thursday – one day earlier than expected – after having them leaked during a livestream of EA Sports' new College Football 25 video game.

item.description: Purdue unveiled new uniforms on Thursday that feature a striping pattern inspired by the Boilermakers' helmets under legendary coach Joe Tiller.
